com.googlecode.javastar
Class AstarResult<N extends Node,C extends Cost<C>>

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.javastar.AstarResult<N,C>

public class AstarResult<N extends Node,C extends Cost<C>>
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents the result of an A star calculation.
The following always holds:
getType() == FAIL => ( getCost() == null && getPath() == null )

Author:
Steven Roose
